<h2>ABOUT</h2>
<h3>Citadel Real Estate</h3>
<p>A family oriented neighborhood, the community in Citadel attracts home buyers from all walks of life including the young, growing families and retirees alike.</p>
<p>With the total built-up areas somewhere between 1000 square ft to 2500 square ft Citadel homes for sale predominately comprise of townhouses, single family homes, and condo units.</p>
<p>Though there is no community center here, a community association oversees most of the community-related tasks. The neighborhood has several pathways that lead to the central hub, which is known for its luscious green spaces.</p>
<p>Schools in Citadel include the St. Brigid Catholic School (Elementary and Junior High), the Citadel Park Elementary School, and Arbour Lake School.</p>
<p>St. Brigid falls under the Calgary Catholic School District.</p>
<p>The Citadel Park Elementary School offers schooling from Kindergarten to Grade 4, after which, students are sent to the Arbour Lake School.</p>
</div>
